				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Except for FHBG, all of my games have used the top left corner, since it simplifies sprite drawing and background collision detection where I need the corners. This way, I already have the X of the top left and bottom left, and the Y of the top left and top right without needing to do any math, so it's only two adds rather than two adds plus two subtracts.</div>

